properties.SOILS: Developed from shale/sandstone materials dark grayish brown, grayish brown, brown to dark brown, clay loam to clay
properties.VEGETATION: Forest, shrub, pasture, kaingin, coconut, corn and upland rice
properties.HYDROLOGIC: Well drained, hydraulic conductivity rapid, water holding capacity is medium
properties.SOIL_CHEM: Soils ph is 4.5 to 5.0 OM; nitrogen content is medium to low available phosphorous to exchangeable potassium medium to high, Ca, Mg, BSP, CEC high salinity is favorable low fertility
properties.PHYSIOGRAP: Rolling to moderate by steep slope 30 to 50 percent elevation less than 500 m.
properties.LIMIT: Shallow soil, moderate to severe erosion, low fertility
